 tái xuất tiếp tục mê hoặc khan giả bằng những hành động mạo hiểm nhưng đầy ngộ nghĩnh. Ngoài ra việc lựa chọn cảnh quay đẹp gần như nguyên sinh của Hawai khiến người xem không khỏi thán phục trước vẻ đẹp thơ mộng nơi đây.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"1865","season":null,"vote_average":6.565,"vote_count":14715},"modified":"2024-09-21T10:59:41.000Z","cast":["Johnny Depp","Penélope Cruz","Geoffrey Rush","Ian McShane","Kevin McNally","Sam Claflin","Àstrid Bergès-Frisbey","Stephen Graham","Keith Richards","Richard Griffiths","Greg Ellis","Damian O'Hare","Óscar Jaenada","Anton Lesser","Roger Allam"],"director":["Rob Marshall"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Johnny Depp","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Johnny Depp","tmdb_id":85,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k2xt6EUxQDwYRKIyI4IBdZxfs8n.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/85"},{"name":"Penélope Cruz","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Penélope Cruz","tmdb_id":955,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n5SFgmvJSENQt8poE4qYacUnKOi.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/955"},{"name":"Geoffrey Rush","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Geoffrey Rush","tmdb_id":118,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/npXFjaFQzBNroCEPllGPTZ5IisA.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/118"},{"name":"Ian McShane","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ian McShane","tmdb_id":6972,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qh9RTLbnr128TZLdGuXwUH9mdBM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/6972"},{"name":"Kevin McNally","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kevin McNally","tmdb_id":2449,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1QvG7MbfeWxb4LlZrlR4OtwvB8v.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2449"},{"name":"Sam Claflin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Sam Claflin","tmdb_id":237455,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e5CU4tjCNZFfm7ITmZfzjZse2Bb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/237455"},{"name":"Àstrid Bergès-Frisbey","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Àstrid Bergès-